'''InFamouS eSport''' was a French eSports organization.

== History ==

== Timeline ==
{{TDRight
|name1=2014
|name2=2015
|name3=2016}}
{{TDRight|tab}}<!--2016-->
* March 10, '''InFamouS eSport''' disbands <ref>[https://twitter.com/InFamouS_eSport/status/707943760508936192 Communiqué sur InFamouS eSport] ''twitter.com''</ref>
{{TDRight|tab}}<!--2015-->
* January 21, '''InFamous eSport''' acquires the roster of {{Team|ROG School|size=35px}}. '''[[Darlik]]''', '''[[Caelan]]''', '''[[Raito]]''', '''[[Reakzy]]''', and '''[[L4mouette]]''' join.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/nouvelle-quipe-lol-491.html Nouvelle équipe (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* June 26, '''InFamouS eSport''' acquires the roster of {{Team|PunchLine Esport Club|size=35px}}. '''[[Shemek]]''', '''[[Nerroh]]''', '''[[Nisqy]]''', '''[[Minitroupax]]''', and '''[[Kirdos]]''' join.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/nouvelle-line-up-lol--664.html Nouvelle line-up (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* October 19, {{bl|Techron}} replaces [[Shemek]].<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/lesl-pgw-lol-challenge-709.html L'ESL PGW LoL Challenge - Nos joueurs sont prêts !] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* December 11, [[Minitroupax]] leaves.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/asus-rog-tournament-718.html ASUS ROG Tournament - L'équipe InFamouS. (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* December 30, {{bl|Phaxi}} and {{bl|Crownie}} join.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/nouvelles-recrues-lol-721.html Nouvelles recrues LoL - De nouveaux infâmes parmis nous ! (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
{{TDRight|tab}}<!--2014-->
* January 3, '''InFamous eSport''' announces LoL Team. '''[[Maximus]]''', '''[[GstP]]''', '''[[SyGn]]''', '''[[Over (French Player)|Over]]''', and '''[[AsterZ]]''' join.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/league-of-legends-23.html InFamouS.LoL rejoint nos rangs ! (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* February 4, [[GstP]] and [[AsterZ]] leave while '''[[Talic]]''' and '''[[Kazujapo]]''' join.<ref>[http://www.infamous.fr/news/infamous.lol-66.html Deux nouvelles recrues (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* April 2, '''InFamous eSport''' acquires a new roster. '''[[Riku (Mickael H.)|Riku]]''', '''[[NoMoreHeroes]]''', '''[[nvious]]''', '''[[Myw]]''', and '''[[Ynkzzz]]''' join.<ref>
[http://www.infamous.fr/news/infamous.lol-146.html Retour sur la scène (French)] ''infamous.fr''</ref>
* April 20, Roster of '''InFamous eSport''' disbands.
{{TDRight/end}}

